// 69_release_board_file
// Concepts: object-root TOON parsing, score normalization, lane classification,
// blocked flag, custom stats type, formatted average
// expect: release 0: R1 / green / false / 92
// expect: release 1: R2 / yellow / true / 76
// expect: release 2: R3 / red / false / 61
// expect: release 3: R4 / green / true / 100
// expect: green = 2
